  "dialogue": {
    "23": {
      "id": "23",
      "speaker": "Gale",
      "text": "What's on your mind?",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "14",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "0": {
          "id": "0",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "My memories before the nautiloid are shrouded in darkness.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "NIGHT_DarkUrge_IsobelKillOrder = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_NoMemories = False",
            "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_NoMemories"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "11": {
              "id": "11",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "Total amnesia isn't usually a symptom of ceremorphosis. If it is, they've forgotten to write it down in any text I've read on the subject.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Curious, trying to see if an answer springs to mind",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "8": {
                  "id": "8",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "Then again, our case isn't exactly usual. Perhaps whatever's causing our tadpoles to remain in stasis has also affected your mind.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Curious, trying to see if an answer springs to mind",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "12": {
                      "id": "12",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "If ceremorphosis takes place, all trace of your former self will be subsumed into the mind flayer's hive. So, to still be here, if a mite forgetful? Still a win in my book.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Cheerfully delivering a terrifying thought",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "28": {
          "id": "28",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I have violent thoughts. Depraved thoughts. Ones that refuse to go away...<br>",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "NIGHT_DarkUrge_IsobelKillOrder = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_Violent = False",
            "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_Violent"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "29": {
              "id": "29",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "We all have those from time to time.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Not taking it very seriously",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "14",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "15": {
                  "id": "15",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "I once wished a most impure demise on a colleague of mine who bought the last remaining copy of Etheril's Enchiridion of Enchanting Easements. First edition, too.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Almost tutting/shaking his head. A disappointing memory.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "14",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "As regards to your own morbid little fantasies, I'm sure they're nothing to worry about. So long as they remain fantasies.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "24": {
          "id": "24",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I swear, what happened to Alfira - it wasn't my fault.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_MurderOfAlfira_Alternative = False",
            "NIGHT_DarkUrge_IsobelKillOrder = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_SuspectedAlfiraMurder",
            "NIGHT_DarkUrge_MurderOfAlfira",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_ProtestedAlfira = False",
            "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_ProtestedAlfira"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "6": {
              "id": "6",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "I'm sure that will be of small comfort to her.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "14",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "21": {
          "id": "21",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "I tried to kill you in my sleep. What if I do it again?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_BhaalResisted = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_BhaalAccepted = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_SparedIsobelWithGale",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_BhaalDisappointed = False",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_WorriedSparedIsobel = False",
            "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_WorriedSparedIsobel"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "7": {
              "id": "7",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "I can hardly hold you responsible for what you do while unconscious, but still... I'll sleep with one eye open. Better safe than, well, dead.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Slightly nervous, but not wanting to hurt or offend you",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "14",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "16": {
          "id": "16",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "What did you make of my improved form?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_State_GivenSlayerForm",
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_BraggedSlayerForm = False",
            "REALLY_DARK_URGE"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "ORI_DarkUrge_Knows_BraggedSlayerForm"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "26": {
              "id": "26",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "Honestly, I didn't know you had it in you. A dark destroyer in our midsts.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "32": {
                  "id": "32",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "It's certainly one of the more unsightly shape-shiftings I've seen, but we can't all be blessed with the elegance of an aasimar transforming in the heavens, can we?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "2": {
                      "id": "2",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "Beggars can't be choosers. Such a powerful form should serve us well in the chaos to come.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "14": {
                          "id": "14",
                          "speaker": "",
                          "text": "",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
